---
// HallucinationScale.astro — Scale/metrics of hallucination problem
---
<div class="hs-wrap">
  <h3 class="hs-title">How Bad Is It?</h3>
  <div class="hs-bars">
    <div class="hs-row"><span class="hs-label">GPT-4 (factual Q&A)</span><div class="hs-bar"><div class="hs-fill hs-fill--1" style="--w:15%"></div></div><span class="hs-val">~15% error rate</span></div>
    <div class="hs-row"><span class="hs-label">GPT-3.5 (factual Q&A)</span><div class="hs-bar"><div class="hs-fill hs-fill--2" style="--w:35%"></div></div><span class="hs-val">~35% error rate</span></div>
    <div class="hs-row"><span class="hs-label">Open-source 7B models</span><div class="hs-bar"><div class="hs-fill hs-fill--3" style="--w:52%"></div></div><span class="hs-val">~52% error rate</span></div>
    <div class="hs-row"><span class="hs-label">Any model + RAG grounding</span><div class="hs-bar"><div class="hs-fill hs-fill--4" style="--w:8%"></div></div><span class="hs-val">~5-8% error rate</span></div>
    <div class="hs-row"><span class="hs-label">Model + RAG + verification</span><div class="hs-bar"><div class="hs-fill hs-fill--5" style="--w:3%"></div></div><span class="hs-val">~2-3% error rate</span></div>
  </div>
  <div class="hs-note">Source: Benchmarks from TruthfulQA, HaluEval, and internal testing. Exact numbers vary by domain and prompt design.</div>
</div>
<style>
  .hs-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0;border:1px solid #334155}
  .hs-title{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 1.5rem}
  .hs-bars{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;margin-bottom:1rem}
  .hs-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;opacity:0;animation:hsIn .4s ease forwards}
  .hs-row:nth-child(1){animation-delay:.1s}.hs-row:nth-child(2){animation-delay:.2s}.hs-row:nth-child(3){animation-delay:.3s}.hs-row:nth-child(4){animation-delay:.4s}.hs-row:nth-child(5){animation-delay:.5s}
  @keyframes hsIn{to{opacity:1}}
  .hs-label{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.7rem;width:160px;flex-shrink:0}
  .hs-bar{flex:1;height:8px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.3);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden}
  .hs-fill{height:100%;border-radius:6px;width:0;animation:hsFill 1.2s ease forwards}
  .hs-fill--1{background:#f59e0b;animation-delay:.3s}.hs-fill--2{background:#f87171;animation-delay:.4s}.hs-fill--3{background:#ef4444;animation-delay:.5s}.hs-fill--4{background:#4ade80;animation-delay:.6s}.hs-fill--5{background:#06b6d4;animation-delay:.7s}
  @keyframes hsFill{to{width:var(--w)}}
  .hs-val{color:#64748b;font-size:.6rem;font-family:monospace;width:90px;text-align:right;flex-shrink:0}
  .hs-note{color:#475569;font-size:.6rem;font-style:italic;text-align:center}
</style>
